title: The Anthony Cumia Show 2014-08-14
description:
Thursday, August 14, 2014

Today kicks off with Anthony recapping Wednesday's wild show with Mary Jean and then gets into conversation and video regarding the overnight rallies in Ferguson, a "peace concert shooting" in Philadelphia, sports stars rapping, and he ends the hour dissecting the types of gals that Charles Manson prefers. Hour two begins with some hit and miss phone calls, examines the diversity in law enforcement, and taps into his love of drones. Ant ends the show with an old home movie showcasing his "pissy eyes", brother Joe calls in, and we view the newest cringe worthy Prancercise video.
